<h4><a href="http://news.mydrivers.com/1/709/709169.htm">华为宣布 IFA 活动时间</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1360519" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/huawei-1.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="337" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/huawei-1.jpg 600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/huawei-1-360x202.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
